,"line":26},{"w":"Thanks","s":183.24,"e":183.4,"line":27},{"w":"for","s":183.4,"e":183.42,"line":27},{"w":"watching","s":183.42,"e":183.56,"line":27}],"lines":[{"s":2.36,"e":12.22,"text":"Don't just aim at the sky Pick one light and tell it why"},{"s":16,"e":21.48,"text":"Pick one star, know its name Trace its fire, feed its flame"},{"s":22.58,"e":30.44,"text":"Not somewhere, not someday Choose one light and cut your way"},{"s":30.44,"e":37.04,"text":"Pick one star, bright and far Point your heart at where you are"},{"s":37.4,"e":44.92,"text":"Dreams get real when targets are clear One true star can pull you near"},{"s":44.92,"e":48.56,"text":"Everybody says shoot high But they never draw the map"},{"s":48.56,"e":52.26,"text":"They throw wishes at the night Then wonder where they're at"},{"s":52.26,"e":56.16,"text":"You need numbers, names, and places A road with turns and signs"},{"s":56.16,"e":59.9,"text":"Not a foggy constellation But a mission with a line"},{"s":59.9,"e":63.54,"text":"Say the goal, set the date Write the steps, lift the weight"},{"s":63.54,"e":67.84,"text":"Make it short, make it known Make that far off higher on"},{"s":67.98,"e":73.94,"text":"Pick one star, know its name Trace its fire, feed its flame"},{"s":73.94,"e":83.06,"text":"Not somewhere, not someday Choose one light and cut your way"},{"s":83.06,"e":89.06,"text":"Pick one star, bright and far Point your heart at where you are"},{"s":89.78,"e":97.38,"text":"Dreams get real when targets are clear One true star can pull you near"},{"s":97.38,"e":104.56,"text":"Don't chase every glowing thing Don't drift with every spark"},{"s":104.56,"e":112.36,"text":"Some lights only blind your eyes Some lights lead through dark"},{"s":112.36,"e":116.04,"text":"Pick the one that makes you better Pick the one that makes you build"},{"s":116.04,"e":119.82,"text":"Pick the one that serves the people Pick the one that tests your will"},{"s":119.82,"e":123.98,"text":"Then climb, grind, shine, refine One bright sign inside your mind"},{"s":123.98,"e":127.86,"text":"Fall, cross, and restart Star in the sky, fire in the heart"},{"s":127.86,"e":135.1,"text":"A vague dream fades in the morning A clear dream wakes you up"},{"s":135.1,"e":142.76,"text":"A named star becomes a warning Don't quit when it gets tough"},{"s":142.76,"e":148.76,"text":"Pick one star, know its name Trace its fire, feed its flame"},{"s":150,"e":157.96,"text":"Not somewhere, not someday Choose one light and cut your way"},{"s":157.96,"e":163.76,"text":"Pick one star, bright and far Point your heart at where you are"},{"s":164.92,"e":172.3,"text":"But when the whole sky disappears One true star still brings you near"},{"s":183.24,"e":183.56,"text":"Thanks for watching!"}],"duration":183.60000610351562,"source":"whisper","generatedAt":"2026-05-22T02:32:28.610Z","model":"whisper-1"}